</code></pre> <ul> <li><code>SafeBuffer.hpp</code>: Keeps a recent safe trajectory for fallback if the IPM diverges.</li> <li><code>DualVec.hpp</code>: Automatic-differentiation (AD) variable used to compute Jacobians.</li> <li><code>MathTraits.hpp</code>: Math utilities (<code>max</code>, <code>min</code>, <code>isnan</code>, etc.).</li> <li><code>StaticMatrix.hpp</code>: Compile-time sized matrices/vectors (used for Riccati Solver).</li> <li><code>Integrator.hpp</code>: RK4 integration for the plant model.</li> <li><code>KKTMonitor.hpp</code>: Computes infinity-norm of the KKT residual.</li> <li><code>RiccatiSolver.hpp</code>: Solves the KKT linear system via Riccati recursion.</li> <li><code>RealTimeDynamicsModel.hpp</code>: Default plant model (e.g., bicycle model).</li> </ul> <p>The main class is located inside <code>namespace nmpc::controller</code>.</p>

1. Preparation2. Stage Cost3. Barrier Terms4. Obstacle Avoidance5. Dynamics Consistency <pre><code>matrix::StaticVector&lt;double, Nx&gt; x_curr = X_pred[0];
x_curr.saxpy(alpha, riccati.dx[0]);

for (std::size_t i = 0; i &lt; Nx; ++i) { // (1)
    merit += L1_WEIGHT * std::abs(x_curr(i) - x_init(i));
}
</code></pre> <ol> <li>State Deviation Penalty: Evaluates \(\text{pen}_{\text{init}}(\alpha)=\sum_{i=1}^{N_x} w_{\text{L1}}\,\bigl|\,x_{\text{curr},i}-x_{\text{init},i}\bigr|\). The large weight forces the line-search to keep the trajectory close to the true initial state <code>x_init</code>.</li> </ol> <pre><code>double err_d = x_curr(1) - config.target_d[k];
double err_mu = x_curr(2);
// ...
merit += 0.5 * (config.Q_D * err_d * err_d + /*...*/); // (1)
merit += 0.5 * (config.R_Steer * u_cand(0) * u_cand(0) + /*...*/); // (2)
</code></pre> <ol> <li>State Error: Penalizes deviations from the reference trajectory (e.g., lateral offset \(d\), velocity \(v\), yaw rate \(r\)).</li> <li>Control Effort: Penalizes steering and acceleration usage.</li> </ol> <pre><code>auto eval_barrier = [&amp;](double c, double s, double ds) {
    double s_cand = s + alpha * ds;
    if (s_cand &lt;= 1e-8) s_cand = 1e-8; // (1)
    return -current_mu * std::abs(s_cand) + L1_WEIGHT * std::abs(c + s_cand);
};
</code></pre> <ol> <li>Numerical Safety: Prevents the slack variable from becoming zero or negative, which would cause \(\log(s)\) to be undefined.</li> </ol> <pre><code>double ds = x_curr(0) - obs_pred_s;
if (std::abs(ds) &gt; 20.0) continue; // (1)

// ... calculate c_obs ...
merit += eval_barrier(c_obs, duals[k].obs[i].s, duals[k].obs[i].ds);
</code></pre> <ol> <li>Optimization: Skips evaluating the barrier for obstacles that are too far away longitudinally (\(&gt; 20\text{m}\)).</li> </ol> <pre><code>for (std::size_t i = 0; i &lt; Nx; ++i) { // (1)
    merit += L1_WEIGHT * std::abs((1.0 - alpha) * riccati.d[k](i));
}
</code></pre> <ol> <li>Affine Residual: \(\text{pen}_{\text{dyn},k}(\alpha)= w_{\text{L1}}\;\bigl|(1-\alpha)\,d_k\bigr|\). Prevents the algorithm from taking a step that would violate the linearized dynamics prediction.</li> </ol>

의존성 (Dependencies)설명 (Descriptions) <pre><code>#include "nmpc/Control/SafeBuffer.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Matrix/AD/DualVec.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Matrix/Core/MathTraits.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Matrix/Core/StaticMatrix.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Simulation/Integrator.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Solver/KKTMonitor.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Solver/MeritLineSearch.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Solver/RiccatiSolver.hpp"
#include "nmpc/Dynamics/RealTimeDynamicsModel.hpp"
</code></pre> <ul> <li><code>SafeBuffer.hpp</code>: IPM이 발산할 경우 폴백을 위한 최근의 안전한 궤적을 유지합니다.</li> <li><code>DualVec.hpp</code>: 자코비안을 계산하는 데 사용되는 자동 미분(AD) 변수입니다.</li> <li><code>MathTraits.hpp</code>: 수학 유틸리티 (<code>max</code>, <code>min</code>, <code>isnan</code> 등).</li> <li><code>StaticMatrix.hpp</code>: 컴파일 타임에 크기가 결정되는 행렬/벡터 (리카티 솔버에 사용됨).</li> <li><code>Integrator.hpp</code>: 플랜트 모델을 위한 RK4 적분기.</li> <li><code>KKTMonitor.hpp</code>: KKT 잔차의 무한대 노름(infinity-norm)을 계산합니다.</li> <li><code>RiccatiSolver.hpp</code>: 리카티 재귀를 통해 KKT 선형 시스템을 풉니다.</li> <li><code>RealTimeDynamicsModel.hpp</code>: 기본 플랜트 모델 (예: 자전거 모델).</li> </ul> <p>메인 클래스는 <code>namespace nmpc::controller</code> 내부에 위치합니다.</p>

1. 준비 (Preparation)2. 단계 비용 (Stage Cost)3. 장벽 항 (Barrier Terms)4. 장애물 회피 (Obstacle Avoidance)5. 동역학 일관성 (Dynamics Consistency) <pre><code>matrix::StaticVector&lt;double, Nx&gt; x_curr = X_pred[0];
x_curr.saxpy(alpha, riccati.dx[0]);

for (std::size_t i = 0; i &lt; Nx; ++i) { // (1)
    merit += L1_WEIGHT * std::abs(x_curr(i) - x_init(i));
}
</code></pre> <ol> <li>상태 편차 페널티: \(\text{pen}_{\text{init}}(\alpha)=\sum_{i=1}^{N_x} w_{\text{L1}}\,\bigl|\,x_{\text{curr},i}-x_{\text{init},i}\bigr|\) 를 평가합니다. 큰 가중치는 라인 서치가 궤적을 실제 초기 상태 <code>x_init</code>에 가깝게 유지하도록 강제합니다.</li> </ol> <pre><code>double err_d = x_curr(1) - config.target_d[k];
double err_mu = x_curr(2);
// ...
merit += 0.5 * (config.Q_D * err_d * err_d + /*...*/); // (1)
merit += 0.5 * (config.R_Steer * u_cand(0) * u_cand(0) + /*...*/); // (2)
</code></pre> <ol> <li>상태 오차: 기준 궤적으로부터의 편차(예: 횡방향 오프셋 \(d\), 속도 \(v\), 요 레이트 \(r\))에 페널티를 줍니다.</li> <li>제어 노력: 조향 및 가속도 사용에 페널티를 줍니다.</li> </ol> <pre><code>auto eval_barrier = [&amp;](double c, double s, double ds) {
    double s_cand = s + alpha * ds;
    if (s_cand &lt;= 1e-8) s_cand = 1e-8; // (1)
    return -current_mu * std::abs(s_cand) + L1_WEIGHT * std::abs(c + s_cand);
};
</code></pre> <ol> <li>수치적 안전성: 여유 변수가 0이 되거나 음수가 되어 \(\log(s)\)가 정의되지 않는 상황을 방지합니다.</li> </ol> <pre><code>double ds = x_curr(0) - obs_pred_s;
if (std::abs(ds) &gt; 20.0) continue; // (1)

// ... calculate c_obs ...
merit += eval_barrier(c_obs, duals[k].obs[i].s, duals[k].obs[i].ds);
</code></pre> <ol> <li>최적화: 종방향으로 너무 멀리 있는(\(&gt; 20\text{m}\)) 장애물에 대해서는 장벽 평가를 건너뜁니다.</li> </ol> <pre><code>for (std::size_t i = 0; i &lt; Nx; ++i) { // (1)
    merit += L1_WEIGHT * std::abs((1.0 - alpha) * riccati.d[k](i));
}
</code></pre> <ol> <li>아핀 잔차 (Affine Residual): \(\text{pen}_{\text{dyn},k}(\alpha)= w_{\text{L1}}\;\bigl|(1-\alpha)\,d_k\bigr|\). 선형화된 동역학 예측을 위반하는 스텝을 밟는 것을 방지합니다.</li> </ol>
